       ["self"],
       true,
       "threading.Semaphore.__enter__.__code__.co_varnames[0].__eq__('self') == True — Semaphore.__enter__ is the context manager entry method defined in Lib/threading.py; it delegates to acquire; its first parameter is 'self'; co_varnames[0] is 'self'; str.__eq__('self') returns True; new to extra127"]
    - [semaphore_enter_co_argcount_eq_3,
